msgid "# Get-ClusterGroup"
msgstr "# Get-ClusterGroup"

msgid "## SYNOPSIS"
msgstr "## 概要"

msgid ""
"Gets information about one or more clustered roles (resource groups) in a "
"failover cluster."
msgstr "获取有关故障转移集群中一个或多个聚类角色（资源组）的信息。"

msgid "## SYNTAX"
msgstr "## 语法"

msgid "## DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "## 描述"

msgid ""
"The `Get-ClusterGroup` cmdlet gets information about one or more clustered roles (resource groups)\n"
"in a failover cluster."
msgstr "`Get-ClusterGroup` cmdlet 可以获取有关故障转移集群中的一个或多个集群角色（资源组）的信息。"

msgid ""
"A resource group is the unit of failover. During failover, all resources in the resource group move\n"
"together."
msgstr "资源组是故障转移的基本单位。在发生故障转移时，资源组中的所有资源会一起被迁移（或重新分配）到其他位置。"

msgid "## EXAMPLES"
msgstr "## 示例"

msgid "### Example 1"
msgstr "### 示例 1"

msgid ""
"This example lists the state and owner node of each clustered role, or resource group, in the local\n"
"cluster."
msgstr "这个示例列出了本地集群中每个集群化角色（或资源组）的状态和所属节点信息。"

msgid "### Example 2"
msgstr "### 示例 2"

msgid ""
"This example lists the resources in `Cluster Group` on the local cluster."
msgstr "这个示例列出了本地集群中“Cluster Group”中的资源。"

msgid "### Example 3"
msgstr "### 示例 3"

msgid ""
"This example lists the clustered services and applications, or resource groups, that are currently\n"
"owned by `node1` in the local cluster."
msgstr "这个示例列出了当前由 `node1` 拥有的、位于本地集群中的服务、应用程序或资源组。"

msgid "### Example 4"
msgstr "### 示例 4"

msgid ""
"This example displays the properties of a clustered file server, or resource group, called\n"
"`FileServer1`, in the form of a list."
msgstr "这个示例以列表的形式展示了名为`FileServer1`的集群文件服务器或资源组的属性。"

msgid "## PARAMETERS"
msgstr "## 参数"

msgid ""
"Specifies the name of the cluster on which to run this cmdlet. If the input for this parameter is\n"
"`.` or it is omitted, then the cmdlet runs on the local cluster."
msgstr "指定用于运行此cmdlet的集群名称。如果该参数的值为`.`或被省略，则cmdlet将在本地集群上运行。"

msgid ""
"Specifies the cluster or cluster node on which to enumerate the clustered "
"roles."
msgstr "指定用于遍历集群角色的集群或集群节点。"

msgid "Specifies the name of the clustered role to get."
msgstr "指定要获取的集群角色的名称。"

msgid "Specifies the virtual machine identifier (ID)."
msgstr "指定虚拟机标识符（ID）。"

